<note n="0180004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0180004">唯＝惟【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0180005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0180005">世尊說＝是世尊【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0180006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0180006">於＝有【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0181001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0181001">愧＝怖【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0181002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0181002">今＝令【明】</note>
<note n="0181003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0181003">修集＝修習【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0183001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0183001">栴＝旃【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0183002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0183002">曰＋（如是說者）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0185001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0185001">如是說者＝評曰【三】【宮】</note>
